{
  "id": "adv_card_mei_09_01",
  "title": "早坂芽衣 1話 恋する少女、早坂芽衣",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-evening",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ある日の打ち合わせにて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――At a meeting one day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "えー！？　芽衣がもし恋のヒロインに選ばれたの！？\n怜ちゃんと渚ちゃんが出てたやつだよね！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whaaat!? Mei was chosen as the heroine of Moshikoi!?\nIt’s that game Rei-chan and Nagisa-chan appeared‚ right!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。夏休み前の忙しいところ申し訳ないが\nぜひ芽衣に協力してほしいとのことだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. Sorry to ask this of you when you’re busy before summer vacation‚\nbut they’d really like your cooperation‚ Mei.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "楽しそう！　芽衣にやらせて！\nあのゲームのヒロインになれるなんて嬉しいな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That sounds fun! Let Mei do it!\nI’m so happy to be the heroine of that game～！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣も怜ちゃんみたいに、最初は冷たいけど\n実は優しい子っていう設定だったりして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe Mei’s like Rei-chan‚ cold at first\nbut actually kind on the inside!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.8999988556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "渚ちゃんみたいな、幼なじみっていう設定もいいよね\n朝から家に「おはよー」って起こしに行くの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A childhood friend setting like Nagisa-chan would be nice too!\nI’ll go to his house in the morning and wake him up with a “Good morning”!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.2999988556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "ねえねえ、{user}さん！\n芽衣のお話はどんな感じになるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ hey‚ {user}-san!\nWhat will Mei’s story be like?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.2999988556,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6610.001144399995,
          "startTime": 49.91
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そのことなんだが\nまずはこの書類に目を通してほしいんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "About that‚\nI want you to look over this document first.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.4666655223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "えっと、これはアンケート？\n恋愛観に、好きなシチュエーション……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um… Is this a survey?\nViews on love‚ favorite situations…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.2333321889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "理想のデートに、告白について……\nこれに書いたことが、そのままゲームになるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ideal date‚ and confession…\nSo the things I write here will be in the game?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.1999988556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "さすがに全部とまではいかないだろうが\n芽衣の意向をなるべく尊重したいと先方は言っていたな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I doubt everything will be included‚ but\nthey said they want to respect your wishes as much as possible.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.0666655223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんだ！　よーっし、頑張って埋めちゃうよ！\nでも、恋愛観って何を書けばいいんだろう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really! Alright~! I’ll fill it out!\nBut what should I write for “views on love”?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.6666655223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "こういう恋愛がしてみたい、とか\n芽衣が思う理想の恋愛について書いてくれればいいぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Like‚ what kind of relationship you’d like to have‚ or…\nyou can just write about your ideal romance‚ Mei.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.7999988556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "理想の恋愛か～\nうーん……何かあるかなぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ideal romance…\nHmm… I wonder what I should write…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.0666655223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "む、難しいなぁ……むむむむ……\nこれ、寮に持って帰って、もう少し考えてみてもいい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "T-this is hard… Hmmmm…\nCan I take this back to the dorm and think about it some more?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.9999988556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "急ぎじゃないから、それでも構わないよ\nじっくり考えてきてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s not urgent‚ so that’s fine.\nTake your time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.9333321889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The next day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.1922056119,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 125.1922056119
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 125.1922056119
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-mei011.m4a",
      "text": "アンケート全部埋めてきたよ～！　理想の恋愛とか\n理想のデートとか、しっかり書いてきたよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I filled out the whole survey~! I wrote about my ideal romance‚\nideal date‚ and everything!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.2000059764,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5329.994023599994,
          "startTime": 135.53
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 133.6205497663
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう。どれどれ……ん？\n「お菓子のお家を一緒に作る」……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks. Let’s see… Hm?\n“Make a gingerbread house together”… ?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.1333393097,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-mei012.m4a",
      "text": "凄く楽しそうでしょ？　好きな人と一緒に\n二人の大好きなお菓子を使ってお家を作るの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It sounds like a lot of fun‚ right? Making a house with\nyour favorite person‚ using both of your favorite sweets!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.2333393097,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 150.0694613696
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣はドーナツで作る、と。確かに楽しそうだが……\nこれが……芽衣の考える理想の恋愛……か？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’d make it with donuts. It does sound fun‚ but…\nis this… your idea of an ideal romance… ?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.566672643,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-mei013.m4a",
      "text": "うん！　『理想の恋愛』って、どういうことかなーって\n芽衣なりに、いーっぱい考えてみたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah! Mei reeeally thought hard in her own way\nabout what “ideal romance” means.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.7333393097,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 171.1549036266
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-mei014.m4a",
      "text": "好きな人と、楽しいことを一緒にするって恋愛っぽい\nでしょ？　それにゲームだし、夢があったらいいなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Doing something fun together with the person you like… That sounds like\na romance‚ right? And it’s a game‚ so it should be dreamy!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.7736046612,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 179.7866950911
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "な、なるほど……\nこの「猫ちゃんの集会に参加する」というのは？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I see…\nAnd what’s this “attend a cat gathering”?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 181.466672643,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-mei015.m4a",
      "text": "夜の公園で、猫ちゃん達がよく集まってるでしょ？\nそこに二人で参加するの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You know how cats often gather in the park at night?\nWe’d go there together!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 189.8304944113,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 192.4295069616
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-mei016.m4a",
      "text": "近所の公園でも、たまに集まってるのをみるんだ～\nそうだ！　猫ちゃんの言葉が話せたらもっと楽しいよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see them gathering sometimes at the park near my house~.\nThat’s right! It would be even more fun if we could speak cat language!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 196.4894612473,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 201.4157881022
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
